metadata.name: NOT TODAY
metadata.description:
Uninhibited is the natural state of everything important.

I`m so excited to present for you the first of 7 works in the collection, that I have given most of myself over the past year. These works appeared thanks to my experiments in the traditional, digital and tattoo art. No boundaries, release of energy and experimentation - is the oxygen for me.

Stay tuned for my next NFT drop from this project and let's get everyone involved!
